description: Share Mii is the first snowy ice truck to proudly serve Orange County and all of Southern California. Share Mii's Snowy Ice takes average shaved ice and elevates it to a cloud like experience. Snowy Ice is a dessert that combines fresh fruit toppings and classic sweets with an ice that is so finely shaved it can only be described as 'Snowy.' "Creamy yet light, softer than your pillow, cut with a ribbon like texture."Welcome to the world of ShareMii!!
name: Share Mii
